Advantages of the Strategy Pattern ğŸŒŸ
1. Flexibility:

We can switch between different payment strategies at runtime without modifying the PaymentProcessor class. ğŸ”„

2. Maintainability:

New payment methods can be added by simply creating new strategy classes. We don't need to touch the existing code. ğŸ› ï¸

3. Separation of Concerns:

Each payment method has its own class, making the code easier to understand and maintain. ğŸ§¹

4. Extensibility:

As new payment methods become available, we can simply add them by creating new strategy classes. ğŸ’¡


